OL,3,CGuernsey Budget 2025: How will
OL,4,Cproposals affect islanders?
OL,6,FStates of Guernsey has outlined its
OL,7,Fproposals for next year's budget.
OL,9,FThe decision comes as the forecasted
OL,10,Fbudget surplus for 2024 has now turned
OL,11,Finto a projected #24 million deficit.
OL,13,FTo raise additional revenues, the
OL,14,FCommittee for Policy and Resources
OL,15,F(P&R) has proposed to increase income
OL,16,Ftax by 2%.
