OL,3,CGuernsey Budget 2025: How will
OL,4,Cproposals affect islanders?
OL,6,FHowever, several other budgetary
OL,7,Ffactors could affect Guernsey
OL,8,Fresidents, despite BDO's Tax Director,
OL,9,FMark Savage, saying more drastic
OL,10,Fchanges might be needed.
OL,12,FHe explains: "Looking at the budget as
OL,13,Fa whole, I was quite surprised by how
OL,14,Fradical it wasn't. Apart from the
OL,15,Fheadline income tax rises, most taxes
OL,16,Fare rising by inflation or potentially
OL,17,Fless.
