OL,6,F"If you look for the budget for next
OL,7,Fyear as proposed ` even stripping out
OL,8,Fthe income tax rise, what you would be
OL,9,Fleft with is a small operating surplus.
OL,11,F"But we are looking to spend 16
OL,12,Fmillion on infrastructure and
OL,13,Finvestments and that would tip us from
OL,14,Fa surplus into a deficit and that's
OL,15,Fbeen going on for a number of years
OL,16,Fand is likely to continue for a number
OL,17,Fof years."
