OL,3,CGuernsey Budget 2025: How will
OL,4,Cproposals affect islanders?
OL,6,FIn an announcement that many Guernsey
OL,7,Fresidents were expecting, income tax
OL,8,Fwill increase by 2% for a limited
OL,9,Fperiod of two years under proposals.
OL,11,FIt means earners will pay an
OL,12,Fadditional 2p for every pound they
OL,13,Fearn.
OL,15,FStates of Guernsey say they aim to
OL,16,Fcounteract the impact on earners by
OL,17,Fincreasing personal income tax
OL,18,Fallowance to #15,000 - a rise of
OL,19,F#1,100 from the current level.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/11
