OL,3,CGuernsey Budget 2025: How will
OL,4,Cproposals affect islanders?
OL,6,FThey say 80% of households in the
OL,7,Flowest income quartile will be better
OL,8,For no worse off than they are today.
OL,10,FDeputy Lyndon Trott, Policy and
OL,11,FResources (P&R) President, defended
OL,12,Fthe rise saying: "It is the prudent
OL,13,Fthing to do and we are crying out for
OL,14,Fmore investment in infrastructure and
OL,15,Fthis will enable that as well."
OL,17,FP&R believes the income tax rise will
OL,18,Fraise additional revenues of #34
OL,19,Fmillion each year.
