OL,6,FHowever, Mark Savage warns: "People
OL,7,Fmight leave money that they don't need
OL,8,Fright now in their companies until the
OL,9,Fincome tax rate has gone back to 20
OL,10,Fper cent in order to defer that and
OL,11,Feffectively reduce their overall tax
OL,12,Fliability."
OL,14,FAlcohol Duty
OL,16,FP&R has announced that they want
OL,17,Falcohol duty to be frozen in 2025.
OL,19,FThe decision is to help the struggling
OL,20,Fhospitality sector, which continues to
OL,21,Fbe damaged by rising duty costs.
