OL,3,CGuernsey Budget 2025: How will
OL,4,Cproposals affect islanders?
OL,6,FHowever, brewing businesses could pay
OL,7,Fmore due to a change in the definition
OL,8,Fof small brewers and cider makers.
OL,10,FCurrently, small brewers are defined
OL,11,Fas those who produce less than 20
OL,12,Fmillion litres per annum (5 million
OL,13,Flitres for small cider makers). They
OL,14,Freceive a 50% discount on alcohol duty.
OL,16,FUnder proposals, both limits are being
OL,17,Freduced to 500,000 litres production
OL,18,Fper annum, meaning some brewers might
OL,19,Fnow be exempt from a discount.
