OL,6,FChanges also mean the alcohol duty
OL,7,Fdiscount will be increased to 60%.
OL,9,FThe Budget estimates income on excise
OL,10,Fduty on alcohol will be #16.4 million
OL,11,Ffor 2025.
OL,13,FTobacco and cigarettes
OL,15,FUnder proposals, taxes on tobacco
OL,16,Fproducts will rise by around 13.2% -
OL,17,F10% above inflation and equivalent to
OL,18,Fan additional pound per pack of
OL,19,Fcigarettes.
