OL,6,FThis change is recommended to cover
OL,7,Fthe remainder of 2024 and into next
OL,8,Fyear.
OL,10,FThe Budget adds that Guernsey will
OL,11,Ffollow the UK in bringing a duty on
OL,12,Fnon-disposable e-cigarettes by 2026.
OL,14,FIt states: "Work is ongoing with
OL,15,Fsuppliers, importers and Customs to
OL,16,Fintroduce this as smoothly as
OL,17,Fpossible, and proposals will be
OL,18,Fincluded in the 2026 Budget Report."
