OL,6,FWhile motor fuel duty would rise by
OL,7,F3.2% under proposals, this would align
OL,8,Fwith inflation.
OL,10,FIt's an increase of around 2.7p per
OL,11,Flitre bringing the overall to 86.8p.
OL,13,FP&R considered increasing excise duty
OL,14,Fon marine use fuel but instead decided
OL,15,Fagainst an increase to support the
OL,16,Fisland's fishing fleet.
OL,18,FThe Budget says fuel duty volumes have
OL,19,Fdeclined with increased engine
OL,20,Fefficiency and the move to electric
OL,21,Fvehicles.
